[CERCo 2017]

Hi engineers!

Finally, Chemical Engineering Research Competition (CERCo) 2017 is opened!
CERCo is an opportunity for you who wants to challenge yourself with research and get the prizes.

With the main theme Research and Technology for Sustainable Development Goals, and the subthemes:
1. Renewable Energy Source
2. Sustainable Waste Treatment
3. Membrane Technology Innovation
4. Innovative Material Synthesis
5. Food Resource Sustainability

We invite you to join this great event.
So what are you waiting for?? Register your best team!!
Don't miss this good opportunity and grab the prizes!

Download the form at http://bit.ly/CERCo2017Form
